des:
The Mystic Schooners are part of the New England Collegiate Baseball League (NECBL), a wood-bat summer league for collegiate athletes. Teams are located throughout New England and participate in a 42 game summer schedule between June and August.
Players from all over of the country flock to New England for competitive summer baseball. The Mystic Schooners are able to operate by the extraordinary efforts provided by its members and the local community.
